{"title": "Lateral Single-Arm Triceps Extension", "content": "<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>Sit sideways on the glideboard and hold one handle with the hand furthest to it in front of your chest, elbow bent and palm facing your body.<br><br></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>Slide the glideboard up by pulling the handle back, straightening your arm and allow yourself back down after a short pause.<br><br></li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>Keep your upper arm and upper body in the same position throughout.<br><br></li>\n\t\t\t\t </ul>"}
